{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "迦道夫（Fes限定Ver.） 第2话 失去了心的女儿",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01",
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "祖国灭亡之后，我为了寻求\\n芬罗达的帮助而前往精灵国。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01",
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "年轻时我通过亚罗拉斯与他相识，\\n之后保持着很好的交情。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01",
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "研究世间各类秘术的他\\n也许有办法能让席菈起死回生。\\n那时的我，只有这一根救命稻草了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（把席菈交给芬罗达已经有一段\\n时日了……就算是他也没有办法\\n让人起死回生吗？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120219_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达的侍从",
            "context": "迦道夫大人，\\n令嫒的治疗已经结束了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "非常感谢你们的帮助。\\n席菈她现在……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "你还活着！\\n真的太好了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "怎么了……\\n你为什么不说话？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120219_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达的侍从",
            "context": "芬罗达大人创造的秘术\\n让席菈小姐重新获得了生命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120219_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达的侍从",
            "context": "然而即使重铸血肉，\\n心却已经……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "心……什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "芬罗达……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "之后，芬罗达对\\n一脸迷茫的我进行了说明。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "他以席菈的血为基础生成了\\n全新的肉体并容纳了她的灵魂。\\n新肉体的脉搏开始跳动，\\n席菈也就此重获生命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "然而这副身体却对\\n席菈的灵魂造成了影响。\\n结果，她失去了心，\\n与从前判若两人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "芬罗达不断地向我道歉。\\n但错并不在他，\\n这是上天给弃子民于不顾的我\\n降下的惩罚。可即便如此……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "只要还活着就一定有希望。\\n我们一起想办法，寻回你的心吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120156_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "在那之后我当起了佣兵，\\n开始奔波于各个战场。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120156_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这不光是为了养家糊口，\\n也是为了寻求方法来\\n寻回席菈的心。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "无论走到哪里，\\n只要听说有与心有关的疗法或法术，\\n我都会为席菈尝试。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "尽管全无效果，\\n但我始终相信终有一天能够\\n让她恢复。直到有一次……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这是预付的房钱。\\n我要三个月后才能回来，\\n不过姑且先支付半年的费用。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "在我回来之前，\\n希望你能让我女儿住在这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "旅馆老板娘",
            "context": "要住在这里的就是她吗？\\n一脸呆滞的样子，有些渗人啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "她只是不能说话，\\n但是能听懂别人说话，不影响日常生活。\\n所以应该不会给你添什么麻烦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈，我又要离开一段时间去战场了。\\n你要好好等我回来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "那一场战争相当惨烈。\\n我所在的阵营陷入苦战，\\n大多数士兵都丢了性命。\\n即便如此，为了回到席菈的身边，\\n我仍奋力迎战。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "将军",
            "context": "唔……我军被压制住了！\\n没有人能扭转战局吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "女儿还在等着我回去，\\n让我来尽快结束这场战事吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "将军",
            "context": "噢噢！“闪狼迦道夫”果然名不虚传！\\n敌军的阵线被冲破了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "突破口已经打开！随我进攻！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "将军",
            "context": "迦道夫阁下，多亏了你，我军才能得救。\\n我衷心地向你表示感谢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "不用谢我，\\n我只是尽了佣兵该尽的义务。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "将军",
            "context": "你也太谦虚了。\\n话说侦察兵来报说发现了敌人的据点。\\n我想拜托你领兵攻下那里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我与你们的契约只有这场平原之战。\\n我的女儿还在等着我回去。\\n所以很抱歉，我没办法延长契约。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "将军",
            "context": "我们常年受敌国欺压，\\n如果现在攻下他们的据点，\\n就能扭转局势并终结这场战争。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "将军",
            "context": "求你了。\\n为了让祖国人们从痛苦中解脱，\\n请务必助我们一臂之力……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（我和店长说的三个月之期已近……\\n但我预付了半年的房租。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（应该还够席菈再住三个月。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "好吧……\\n那我就再帮你们一把。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "带领军队获得胜利后，\\n我急忙回到了席菈等着我的旅馆。\\n此时距离我离开已有五个月之久。\\n然而……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "什么叫席菈不见了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "旅馆老板娘",
            "context": "谁知道呢。\\n不知道什么时候就自己跑出去了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "听说席菈所住的房间\\n现在正住着其他的客人。\\n但我给的钱应该是半年份吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "旅馆老板娘",
            "context": "房间正好空着，我就让人住进去了。\\n毕竟我也得做生意嘛。你还有完没完。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我无法接受你的解释。\\n希望你能和我说实话。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我除了这个女儿已经一无所有了。\\n如果连她也失去的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我可不能保证我不会做出什么事来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "旅馆老板娘",
            "context": "唔……其实是房间住满的时候，\\n有一位客人愿意支付双倍的费用。\\n所以就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "所以你为了钱就把席菈赶走了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "旅馆老板娘",
            "context": "你、你那么长时间都不回来，\\n我还以为你已经战死了！\\n那我也没必要对死人遵守承诺啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "旅馆老板娘",
            "context": "我可是先声明啊，\\n是你的女儿自己同意并离开的！\\n就算有什么事也是她自己的问题！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我并不打算和你讨论这个问题。\\n我只想知道，席菈去哪了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈，你在哪儿！？\\n听到的话就回答我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（根据老板娘的说法，\\n席菈应该是来了这片森林才是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "刚刚那是……魔兽的咆哮声！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈！哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
